# User Story
### Essential components
- [ ] Stakeholder type is identified
- [ ] Outcome is described
- [ ] Rationale is explicit
- [ ] Acceptance criteria are verifiable and from the perspective of the stakeholder

## Story
As a developer
I want an evaluation of Apache Maven
so that a build environment can be established per User Story #2

## Acceptance Criteria

* An evaluation of relevant characteristics of Maven exists in the repository
* The comparison articulates attributes and behaviors in the specific context of this project
* The evaluation cites authoritative references

## Issues Dependent on This User Story

User Story #2
